channel.title: Roll Cage for Ford-150
channel.description: Hi, My name is Leo and I have completed the electrical modifications for my first car (Ford-150). I am looking for assistance as it relates to completing the car. I had an instruction manual for the electrical mods, is there a manual for the PVC roll cage and safety modifications? If not, I would love it if someone could zoom with me a couple times to assist and guide me in completing the car.
